name: ILLICIT LOVE
description:
The saga continues. Violy didn't know that the Prince of Darkness was already aware of her affair with The Reaper.
Satan's eyes saw all the titillating acts that the Witch and Death committed. He watched as his heart pounds, his brow furrowed and teeth clenched.
He had enough. He can't take it anymore. He will once again step down his throne to challenge the Angel of Death to one final battle.
Whoever stands victorious wins the heart of the Enchantress.

The Pale Death accepted.

Little did they know neither of them will win. They don't know that The Violy always wins.
